n: Holly's Chocolate Chip Cookie Dough Dip
des: "This is a quick, easy and fun twist on the great taste everyone loves, chocolate chip cookie dough!  Serve this 5 minute dip with graham crackers or vanilla wafers for a treat young and old will enjoy."
ins:
Beat together cream cheese, butter, confectioners' sugar, brown sugar and vanilla in a bowl.
Stir in chocolate chips.
Refrigerate until ready to serve.
